  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="2CH 9:1" />And when the <char style="w" strong="H4436">queen</char> of <char style="w" strong="H7614">Sheba</char> <char style="w" strong="H8085">heard</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H8088">fame</char> of <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char>, she <char style="w" strong="H0935">came</char> to <char style="w" strong="H5254">prove</char> <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char> with hard <char style="w" strong="H2420">questions</char> at <char style="w" strong="H3389">Jerusalem</char>, with a <char style="w" strong="H3966">very</char> <char style="w" strong="H3515">great</char> <char style="w" strong="H2428">company</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H1581">camels</char> that <char style="w" strong="H5375">bare</char> <char style="w" strong="H1314">spices</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H2091">gold</char> in <char style="w" strong="H7230">abundance</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H3368">precious</char> <char style="w" strong="H0068">stones</char>: and when she was <char style="w" strong="H0935">come</char> to <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char>, she <char style="w" strong="H1696">communed</char> with him of all that was in her <char style="w" strong="H3824">heart</char>. <verse eid="2CH 9:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="2CH 9:2" />And <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">told</char> her all her <char style="w" strong="H1697">questions</char>: and there was nothing <char style="w" strong="H5956">hid</char> from <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char> which he <char style="w" strong="H5046">told</char> her not. <verse eid="2CH 9:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="2CH 9:3" />And when the <char style="w" strong="H4436">queen</char> of <char style="w" strong="H7614">Sheba</char> had <char style="w" strong="H7200">seen</char> the <char style="w" strong="H2451">wisdom</char> of <char style="w" strong="H8010">Solomon</char>, and the <char style="w