  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="2CH 20:31" />¶ And <char style="w" strong="H3092">Jehoshaphat</char> <char style="w" strong="H4427">reigned</char> over <char style="w" strong="H3063">Judah</char>: <char style="add">he was</char> <char style="w" strong="H7970">thirty</char> and <char style="w" strong="H2568">five</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">years</char> <char style="w" strong="H1121">old</char> when he began to <char style="w" strong="H4427">reign</char>, and he <char style="w" strong="H4427">reigned</char> <char style="w" strong="H6242">twenty</char> and <char style="w" strong="H2568">five</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">years</char> in <char style="w" strong="H3389">Jerusalem</char>. And his <char style="w" strong="H0517">mother’s</char> <char style="w" strong="H8034">name</char> <char style="add">was</char> <char style="w" strong="H5806">Azubah</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1323">daughter</char> of <char style="w" strong="H7977">Shilhi</char>. <verse eid="2CH 20:31" /><verse number="32" style="v" sid="2CH 20:32" />And he <char style="w" strong="H3212">walked</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H1870">way</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0609">Asa</char> his <char style="w" strong="H0001">father</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H5493">departed</char> not from it, <char style="w" strong="H6213">doing</char> <char style="add">that which was</char> <char style="w" strong="H3477">right</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H5869">sight</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>. <verse eid="2CH 20:32" /><verse number="33" style="v" sid="2CH 20:33" />Howbeit the high <char style="w" strong="H1116">places</char> were not taken <char style="w" strong="H5493">away</char>: for as yet the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char> had not <char style="w" strong="H3559">prepared</char> their <char style="w" strong="H3824">hearts</char> unto the <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> of their <char s